{
  "chapter": "063",
  "title": "老子韩非列传",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "老子其人",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">老子</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">苦县</span>厉乡曲仁里人，姓<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">李氏</span>，名<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李耳\">耳（李耳）</span>，字摐，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>朝守藏室的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">史</span>官。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "孔子问礼",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔子</span>前往<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>都，将要向<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">老子</span>请教<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">礼</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">老子</span>说：\"您所提到的那些人，连同他们的骨头都早已腐朽了，只剩下他们的言论而已。而且<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">君子</span>遇上好时机就驾车出仕，遇不上就像蓬草一样随风飘转。我听说，善于经商的人〘※深藏若虚〙，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">君子</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">德</span>行充盈其容貌却显得愚笨。去掉您的骄气和过多欲望、矫饰的神态和放纵的志向吧，这些对您自身都没有好处。我能告诉您的，就是这些而已。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔子</span>离去后，对<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟子</span>们说：\"<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">鸟</span>，我知道它能飞；<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">鱼</span>，我知道它能游；<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">兽</span>，我知道它能跑。会跑的可以用<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">罔</span>捕，会游的可以用<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">纶</span>钓，会飞的可以用<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">矰</span>射。至于<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">龙</span>，我不能了解它是如何乘着风云而飞上天的。我<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">今日</span>见到的<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">老子</span>，他就像<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">龙</span>一样啊！\""
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "著书西去",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">老子</span>修<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">道</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">德</span>之学，他的学问以自我隐匿、不求名利为宗旨。在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>都居住久了，见<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>朝衰落，就离开了。到了关口，关口的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">令尹</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：关令尹喜\">喜（关令尹喜）</span>说：\"您将要隐居了，请勉力为我著书吧。\" 于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">老子</span>就写了上下两篇著作，阐述<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">道</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">德</span>的旨意，共<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五千馀</span>言，写完就离去了，没人知道他的结局。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "老莱疑辨",
      "text": "有人说：<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">老莱子</span>也是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国人，著书<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十五</span>篇，论述<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">道家</span>的用处，与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔子</span>同一时代。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "老子后世",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">老子</span>的儿子名叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李宗\">宗（李宗）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李宗\">宗（李宗）</span>做过<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国的将领，被<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">段干</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李宗\">宗（李宗）</span>的儿子叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李注\">注（李注）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李注\">注（李注）</span>的儿子叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李宫\">宫（李宫）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李宫\">宫（李宫）</span>的玄孙叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李假\">假（李假）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李假\">假（李假）</span>在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝文帝</span>时做官。而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李假\">假（李假）</span>的儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李解\">解（李解）</span>做<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">胶西王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘卬\">卬（刘卬）</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太傅</span>，因此就在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>地安家了。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "庄子其人",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄子</span>，是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蒙</span>地人，名叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：庄周\">周（庄周）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：庄周\">周（庄周）</span>曾做过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蒙</span>地漆园的小吏，与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">梁惠王</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐宣王</span>同时代。他的学问无所不窥，然而要旨本归于<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">老子</span>的学说。所以他的著书<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十馀万</span>言，大抵都是寓言。他写<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">渔父</span>、<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">盗跖</span>、<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">胠箧</span>等篇，用来诋毁<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔子</span>之徒，以阐明<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">老子</span>的<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">术</span>。<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">畏累虚</span>、<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">亢桑子</span>之类，都是凭空虚构没有实事。然而他善于行文遣辞，指事类比，借以<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">抨击</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">儒</span>、<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">墨</span>两家，即使当世的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宿学</span>也无法自我解脱。他的文辞汪洋恣肆、任意铺陈以适合自己，所以从<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">王公</span>到<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大人</span>都不能器重他。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "申不害事韩",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">申不害</span>，是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">京</span>地人，本来是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郑</span>国的低贱<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>子。他学了<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">术</span>来求见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩昭侯</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昭侯</span>任用他为相。在内整饬<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">政</span>治<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">教</span>化，对外应付<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，共<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十五年（时长）</span>。终<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">申子</span>一生，国家安定兵力强盛，没有人来侵犯<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "韩非出身",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩非</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公子</span>。他喜好<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">刑名法术</span>之学，而其学问归本于<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">黄老</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩非\">非（韩非）</span>为人口吃，不善于讲话，却擅长著书。他和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李斯</span>一同师事<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">荀卿</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：李斯\">斯（李斯）</span>自认为比不上<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩非\">非（韩非）</span>。"
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "著书立说",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩非\">非（韩非）</span>见<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国衰弱，多次上书劝谏<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>王，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>王却不能采用。于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩非</span>痛恨治国不致力于整饬明确<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">法</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">制</span>、掌握<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">势</span>来驾驭臣下、富国强兵而去求贤任<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">贤</span>，反而起用浮夸淫邪的蛀虫般的人物并把他们置于有功务实者之上。他认为<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">儒者</span>用<span class=\"ritual\" title=\"礼仪\">文</span>乱<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">法</span>，而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">侠者</span>用武犯禁。国家宽松时就宠信有名誉的人，形势紧迫时就任用披甲戴盔的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>。如今所供养的不是所任用的，所任用的不是所供养的。他悲伤廉洁正直之人不被邪曲之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>容纳，观察古往今来的得失变化，所以写出<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">孤愤</span>、<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">五蠹</span>、<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">内外储</span>、<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">说林</span>、<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">说难</span>等共<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十馀万</span>言。"
    },
    "16": {
      "title": "说难全文",
      "text": "<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">说难</span>说："
    },
    "25": {
      "title": "入秦被害",
      "text": "有人把韩非的著作传到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王看到<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">孤愤</span>、<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">五蠹</span>这些书，说：\"唉，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">寡人</span>能见到这个人并与之交游，死也无憾了！\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李斯</span>说：\"这是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩非</span>所写的书。\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国于是急切地<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻打</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>王起初不任用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩非\">非（韩非）</span>，等到情势急迫，才派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩非\">非（韩非）</span>出使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王喜爱他，还没有信任重用。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李斯</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">姚贾</span>妒害他，诋毁他说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩非</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公子</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">今王</span>想兼并<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩非\">非（韩非）</span>最终会为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>国效力而不为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国，这是人之常情。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">今王</span>不任用他，久留而放他回去，这是给自己留下后患，不如依<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">法</span>处罪<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀他。\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王认为有理，把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩非\">非（韩非）</span>交给狱吏治罪。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李斯</span>派人送<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">药</span>给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩非\">非（韩非）</span>，让他<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">自杀</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩非</span>想自己陈述，得不到召见。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王后来后悔，派人去<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">赦免</span>他，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩非\">非（韩非）</span>已经死了。"
    },
    "27": {
      "title": "太史公曰",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">老子</span>所推崇的是<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">道</span>，即<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">虚无</span>，因应<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">变化</span>于<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">无为</span>之中，所以所著之书言辞称<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">微妙</span>而难以理解。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄子</span>发散<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">道</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">德</span>，放言纵论，要旨也归于<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">自然</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">申子</span>用心精细卑微，施用于<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">名实</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩非\">韩子（韩非）</span>引绳墨为度，切中事情实际，明辨<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">是非</span>，其极端处却严酷刻薄而少<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">恩</span>。 这些都源于<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">道</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">德</span>的旨意，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">老子</span>最为深远。"
    },
    "28": {
      "title": "赞",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：老子\">伯阳（老子）</span>创立教化，主张<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">清净</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">无为</span>。 <span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">道</span>尊于东鲁，足迹流窜至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">西垂</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：庄子\">庄（庄子）</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蒙</span>地栩栩而适，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：申不害\">申（申不害）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：申不害\">害（申不害）</span>用心卑卑。 <span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">刑名</span>自有<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">术</span>，<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">说难</span>极尽知辨。 悲叹那<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>防不严，最终竟亡于<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李斯</span>之手。"
    }
  }
}